# Makefile

- First line: comment stating repo name and "follow .cursor/rules.md" (e.g. `# finetuning â€“ follow .cursor/rules.md (proxy, UV, docs/progress.md)`).
- Declare `.PHONY` for all targets at the top.
- Every target: one-line `##` help (e.g. `check-proxy: ## Check that LLM proxy is running`).
- LLM-using targets: depend on `check-proxy` (or equivalent).
- Centralize variables at top (e.g. `PROXY_URL`, `CONFIG_PATH`, `IMAGE_TAG`).
